          "headersSize": 573,
          "httpVersion": "HTTP/1.1",
          "method": "POST",
          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"output\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"topic\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"summary\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"topic\",\"summary\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}}},\"required\":[\"output\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"\\n    <background>\\n      The user and agent have been brainstorming about their business idea.\\n    </background>\\n\\n    <available_topics>\\n      \\\"idea: The core business idea. What does the business do? What makes them different?\\\", \\\"audience: The target audience. What are their pain points? What are their goals?\\\", \\\"solution: How does the user's business solve the audience's pain points, or help them reach their goals?\\\", \\\"socialProof: Social proof or testimonials to include on the landing page. Remember, anything can be social proof: the user's background, experience, beliefs, founder story, etc.\\\", \\\"lookAndFeel: The look and feel of the landing page.\\\"\\n    </available_topics>\\n\\n    <task>\\n      Read the recent chat history, and summarize their answers,\\n      preserving as much information as possible. This will be used to generate \\n      persuasive marketing copy, so be sure to capture all the details.\\n\\n      If the user has answered MULTIPLE topics well, return an array of objects with the following shape:\\n      {\\n          topic: string,\\n          summary: string,\\n      }\\n    </task>\\n    \\n    <chat-history>\\n  <message>... 2 more messages...</message>\\n  <message>assistant: \\\"That's awesome! And what about your social proof?\\\"</message>\\n  <message>human: \\\"Over 10k creators use Friend of the Pod to find guests for their shows.\\\\n    Real case: Host found 3 guests in 10 minutes instead of 5 hours of manual outreach, leading to 2 viral episodes. As the founder of the company, I used to work at Spotify and Apple Podcasts, so I've seen first hand what makes a guest a good fit for a show, and I understand the industry.\\\"</message>\\n</chat-history>\\n\\n    <output>\\n      Return an array of objects with the following shape:\\n      {\\n          topic: string,\\n          summary: string,\\n      }\\n    </output>\\n  \"}]}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 967,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 967,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01WVbhSRS86yzPBcerwApQZZ\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_012EmrwPKBAAWynUBbybX8Tm\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"output\":[{\"topic\":\"socialProof\",\"summary\":\"Over 10k creators actively use Friend of the Pod to find guests for their shows. Real case study: A host found 3 qualified guests in just 10 minutes instead of spending 5 hours on manual outreach, which resulted in 2 viral episodes. Founder has direct industry credibility - previously worked at Spotify and Apple Podcasts, giving firsthand expertise in understanding what makes a guest a good fit for a show and deep knowledge of the podcast industry.\"}]}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1183,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":157,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
