            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1947,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_012Wzo1F3JAtG6tXtqg1rF4w\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate you wanting to move forward, but I need to understand your core business idea first—it's the foundation for everything else we'll build.\\n\\nLet me help you think through this. Here are some examples of what a strong business idea looks like:\\n\\n- **A subscription service for busy parents** that delivers pre-portioned, allergy-friendly meals so they don't have to spend hours meal planning\\n- **An AI-powered resume builder for career changers** that helps non-traditional candidates highlight transferable skills to land interviews at top companies\\n- **A done-for-you social media management service for local plumbers** that generates 3-5 qualified leads per month without them lifting a finger\\n\\nThe key is: **What do you do, and what makes you different?**\\n\\nHere's what I'm looking for:\\n- What problem does your business solve?\\n- Who are you solving it for?\\n- What's your unique angle or approach?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I need to understand your core business idea first. What problem does your business solve, and what makes your approach different from what's already out there?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"A subscription meal service for busy parents with allergy-friendly options\\\",\\n    \\\"An AI resume builder for career changers highlighting transferable skills\\\",\\n    \\\"Done-for-you social media management for local plumbers generating qualified leads\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Tell me about your business idea—what do you do, and what makes you different?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2543,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":345,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
          },
